        <item>
            <title>过往皆是错</title>
            <link>http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_4b56f2d70100natb.html</link>
            <description><![CDATA[<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Century; mso-hansi-font-family: Century; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: en-Us; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn; mso-bidi-language: Ar-sA">
我是近视眼，但度数不深。工作的时候难免要用到隐形眼镜，但总觉得哪里不舒服。最近遇到</SPAN> <span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Century; mso-hansi-font-family: Century; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: en-Us; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn; mso-bidi-language: Ar-sA">
“乐乐音乐乐园”时代的老朋友，他给我推荐了港汇</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: Century; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: en-Us; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn; mso-bidi-language: Ar-sA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">5</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Century; mso-hansi-font-family: Century; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: en-Us; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn; mso-bidi-language: Ar-sA">楼的“艾视迪”，一家隐形眼镜专卖店。据说“口碑很好，值得一去”，就过来试一试，果然长了不少见识。</SPAN></P>
<p><a href="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static7.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4b56f2d7g93c42331f4f6" TARGET="_blank"><img SRC="http://static7.photo.sina.com.cn/middle/4b56f2d7g93c42331f4f6&amp;690" WIDTH="640" HEIGHT="359" /></A><br />
<a href="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static16.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4b56f2d7g93c4256de9ef" TARGET="_blank"><img SRC="http://static16.photo.sina.com.cn/middle/4b56f2d7g93c4256de9ef&amp;690" WIDTH="640" HEIGHT="359" /></A><br />
<span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Century; mso-hansi-font-family: Century; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn">
先是检查眼睛的度数，机器和店员都很专业，让人放心。</SPAN><span STYLE="mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">

</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-ALiGn: left; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt" ALIGN="left"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Century; mso-hansi-font-family: Century; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn">
检查结果，右眼</SPAN><span STYLE="mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">125</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Century; mso-hansi-font-family: Century; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn">，左眼</SPAN><span STYLE="mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">150</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Century; mso-hansi-font-family: Century; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn">。这个度数和我以前检查的完全一致，但是悲剧的是一直以来我居然把左右眼的度数搞反了。也就是说我长久以来一直把</SPAN><span STYLE="mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">150</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Century; mso-hansi-font-family: Century; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn">度的镜片戴在右眼上，</SPAN><span STYLE="mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">125</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Century; mso-hansi-font-family: Century; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn">度的镜片戴在了左眼！因为在其它店买隐形眼镜的时候，从来没有人帮我把左右的标示贴在包装盒上，而我就这样一直反着戴了好几年！</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-ALiGn: left; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt" ALIGN="left"><span STYLE="mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"><span STYLE="LAYoUT-GriD-MoDe: line; FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; CoLor: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-ansi-language: x-none; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn; mso-bidi-language: x-none; mso-font-width: 0%">
接着，店员又帮我做了一个在其它眼镜店我从来没有做过眼睛健康检查。据说这个检查在这家店配镜片前是必须做的，因为有些眼部的疾病我们自己并不一定知道。特别是配戴隐形眼镜，如果眼睛有炎症时是不能戴的。检查出来的结果又给了我打击，我的瞳孔周围因为疲劳充血，而且眼睛还有炎症，可能是受了眼妆的影响。店员说，今后一定要先戴隐形眼镜再化妆，先拿隐形眼镜再卸妆。平时我习惯用小棒子戴隐形眼镜也是不健康的习惯，这会增加交叉感染的机会！</SPAN></SPAN></P>
<p><a href="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static12.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4b56f2d7g93c427090afb" TARGET="_blank"><img SRC="http://static12.photo.sina.com.cn/middle/4b56f2d7g93c427090afb&amp;690" WIDTH="640" HEIGHT="359" /></A><br />
<span STYLE="LAYoUT-GriD-MoDe: line; FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; CoLor: black; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: x-none; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn; mso-bidi-language: x-none; mso-font-width: 0%">
查完散光，又试戴了一下隐形眼镜的样品。让我吃惊的是，店里洗手用的水居然是纯净水而不是普通的自来水，顿时让我心生好感！这个服务贴心！</SPAN><br />

<a href="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static6.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4b56f2d7g93c428454515" TARGET="_blank"><img SRC="http://static6.photo.sina.com.cn/middle/4b56f2d7g93c428454515&amp;690" WIDTH="359" HEIGHT="571" /></A><br />
<span STYLE="LAYoUT-GriD-MoDe: line; FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; CoLor: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-ansi-language: x-none; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn; mso-bidi-language: x-none; mso-font-width: 0%">
这家店是隐形眼镜的专卖店，各种品牌的隐形眼镜都有。以前我都带日抛的彩片，这次和店员交流后才知道，买隐形眼镜最重要是看透氧率，也就是镜片的透气性。日抛的适合短时间配戴，因为它的含水量高。如果是长时间的经常性的，最好不要用彩片和透氧率低的。我平时的不舒服常常就是因为干燥引起的。所以，这次通过店员推荐买的是</SPAN><span STYLE="LAYoUT-GriD-MoDe: line; FonT-FAMiLY: 'Times new roman'; CoLor: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ansi-language: x-none; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn; mso-bidi-language: x-none; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-width: 0%" LANG="X-NONE" XML:LANG="X-NONE">AVAIRA</SPAN><span STYLE="LAYoUT-GriD-MoDe: line; FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; CoLor: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-ansi-language: x-none; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn; mso-bidi-language: x-none; mso-font-width: 0%">（爱维纳）的</SPAN><span STYLE="LAYoUT-GriD-MoDe: line; FonT-FAMiLY: 'Times new roman'; CoLor: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ansi-language: x-none; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn; mso-bidi-language: x-none; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-width: 0%" LANG="X-NONE" XML:LANG="X-NONE">3</SPAN><span STYLE="LAYoUT-GriD-MoDe: line; FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; CoLor: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-ansi-language: x-none; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn; mso-bidi-language: x-none; mso-font-width: 0%">个月普通透明隐形眼镜！透氧率极高！</SPAN></P>
<p><a href="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static8.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4b56f2d7g93c429f087b7" TARGET="_blank"><img SRC="http://static8.photo.sina.com.cn/middle/4b56f2d7g93c429f087b7&amp;690" WIDTH="640" HEIGHT="359" /></A><br />
<span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Century; mso-hansi-font-family: Century; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn">
在上海，包括离电视台很近的四季坊店，好像一共有</SPAN><span STYLE="mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">7</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Century; mso-hansi-font-family: Century; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn">家门店，注册为会员后，无论哪家店都会有我的眼睛数据登记，下次利用时就很方便了！眼睛是五官中很重要的部位，隐形眼镜还是要在能让人放心的店里购买！</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Century; mso-hansi-font-family: Century; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: en-Us; mso-fareast-language: ZH-Cn; mso-bidi-language: Ar-sA">
走的时候，店员主动帮我在购买的隐形眼镜的包装盒上标明了左右眼，还送了小瓶得护理液。今天最大的收获还是学到了不少关于隐形眼镜的知识，很实用！起码从今开始我再也不会把左右眼的镜片带反啦！</SPAN><br />
</P>]]></description>
